{"tid":1569433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙特國營油企兩處石油設施遭無人機襲擊　胡塞武裝認責","createTime":"2019-09-14T15:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T16:34:39.000Z","uid":40250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ff5fb786c730c2612a39bf686e98616932d0ba2d","tid":1569433,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:23:45.000Z","msg":"沙特阿拉伯內政部表示，今早（14日）有無人機攻擊國營石油巨企沙特阿美（Saudi Aramco）位於阿布蓋格（Abqaiq）及胡賴斯（Khurais）兩省的石油設施，導致起火，目前火勢已受控。親伊朗的也門胡塞武裝組織其後承認施襲。<br />\n<br />\n內政部稱，今早凌晨4時，沙特阿美的工業安全隊伍已開始撲滅該兩省受襲設施的大火，目前未知損毁情况。阿布蓋格位於沙特東部省（Eastern Province）達蘭市（Dhahran）西南約60公里處，擁有全球最大石油加工廠；胡賴斯則位於達蘭市更遠的西南方約190公里處，擁有沙特第二大油田。<br />\n<br />\n近月中東區內國家關係緊張，也門胡塞武裝組織上月曾攻擊沙特謝拜（Shaybah）油田設施，5月也攻擊其他石油設施。兩次襲擊均引起火災，但沒有影響石油生產。"},{"pid":"e14985c0c09e1e2173f7e2af30bd3d6d4248ef4b","tid":1569433,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21a53c14ef783a4c7b5b1e75c36cd5134586182a","tid":1569433,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:24:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仆你個臭街！<br />\n今日死差佬同藍絲又周圍打人呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n聽日九月十五日<br />\n<br />\n12pm 金鐘 英領<br />\n2pm 銅鑼灣東角道 /<br />\n維園  </span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全人類同我出黎！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 唔係我屌埋你老母呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/newsfeed/000/915/652/b49.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Fnewsfeed%2F000%2F915%2F652%2